description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'Birth Ball Exercises For Easy Delivery (Third Trimester Exercises For Pregnancy)' from the channel Pregnancy and Postpartum TV.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: These are the birth ball exercises I did daily during third trimester to prepare for an easy delivery and positive birth! You can start these pregnancy exercises at any time, (it's never too early for birth preparation) but of course are most helpful as you get closer to your birth! You can do these third trimester exercise alone or add them on to your pregnancy workout if you have time!
